{ A temporary piece sac. The position becomes very sharp. } 19. Bxe6+ Kb8 20.
Bxg4 { The only way to parry the mate. } 20... hxg4
{ The white king is still in danger. } 21. Nxh8 Rxh8 22. Rf4
{ The white king is ready to run. } 22... Qh1+ 23. Kf2 Qxa1
{ We got back the material. The position is balanced, but I think it's easier to play with Black. The correspondence game Abdulmanov, E 2225 - Eliseev, N 2188 ICCF 2019 continued  24.Qb1  g3+  25.Kf3  Qxb1  26.Nxb1  Bd6  27.Rf6  Rh1  . }
