{ So far it is Postny, E 2630 - Sokolov, I 2623 Montpellier 2015. }
19... Qe7+ { This queen trade is strong here. The endgame favours Black. } 20.
Qxe7+ Bxe7
{ The pieces are to be preferred in this endgame. I think White is in trouble here because we have the bishop pair and also a rook to support the minor pieces. }
