12. e3 { With this move order White forced us to have the bishop on f8. } 12...
Be6
{ We are going for the long castle plan. In my early days with this line I played  12...Bg7  in Palac, M 2571 - Parligras, M 2576 Warsaw 2013, which you can find in the annotated games. }
