10. a3 { Forces the events. } 10... Nxe5 { Forced. } 11. axb4 Nxf3+ 12. gxf3
Qxb4 13. Qd4
{ White offers a queen trade. Until here it was Bu, X 2723 - Predke, A 2535 Sochi 2016. }
13... Qxd4 { The ending is good for us. } 14. exd4 Nc6 15. Ra4 Re8+ 16. Kd2 Rb8
{ An important detail. We can play ...a6 to control the b5-square. Also after  17.Bb5  a6  18.Bxc6  bxc6  the rook will be more than useful on the b-file.   And after  17.Nxd5  Rd8  White doesn't have Nc7 with tempo. The endgame is about equal. }
