{ The wrong pawn move.  18.h3  was good. } 18... Neg4
{ Black got a winning position in Nakamura, H 2784 – Mamedyarov, S 2753 Moscow 2013.The game continued with  19.h3  trying to get rid of the knight  19...Nxf2!  a strong sacrifice  20.Kxf2  Bxh3  White's position is falling apart - ...Ng4 is a threat  21.Kg1  Bxg3  and White resigned a few moves later. }
