{ White has to do something fast until we get back the pawn. If  12.O-O-O  then  12...O-O!  is good, and the white king is exposed. }
12... Be6 { We defend the pawn. } 13. e4
{ Otherwise, we just take back the pawn with ...Nxc5. } 13... dxe4 14. Bxa6
