{ It's important to keep an eye on the c-pawn. Note that  15...Bxa2?  would be wrong due to  16.Nf5! }
16. c6 Bxa2
{ The position is about equal. Our plan is to castle, after which we can bring the bishop to c4-b5 in order to take the c6-pawn. The correspondence game Schultheiss, K 2369 - Schmitt, C 2350 ICCF 2021 ended in a draw a few moves later. }
