15... Rfd8 { Getting ready against e4. } 16. e4 dxe4 17. Nxe4 Qf4
{ A good spot for the queen. } 18. Nxd6 Rxd6
{ Black doesn't have any problem, for example,  19.Rxc7  Nc6  20.Qd3  Nxd4  21.Nxd4  Rxd4  . }
