6. Bxf6 Qxf6 7. e3 { A solid move, simply continuing development. } 7... O-O 8.
Be2
{ This move used to be fashionable, but Black found enough resources against it. The point is to continue development, and if ...dxc4 is played, not to hurry to take the pawn back. }
