{ With an equal position, where there is plenty of play left, of course. The correspondence game Granz, T 2116 - Holland, E 2190 ICCF 2020 ended in a draw after  16.Rfd1  Ba6  17.Ne3  Bxe2  18.Qxe2  cxd4  . After  19.cxd4  Rac8  the game is even. }
