12... Qe7 { We just continue our plan. } 13. Qa4
{ Trying to prevent the knight from getting out. } 13... c5 14. Rab1
{ Was tried in a correspondence game. White just activates the rook. } 14...
cxd4 15. cxd4 Nc6
