{ I like this move back. It points out that the g4-knight is misplaced. } 13.
f4
{ In order to bring the knight to e5.   13.Nxd5??  and White loses material after  13...h5  because the knight is stuck. The knight can't go to e5 because it loses a piece after  14.Ne5   While the desperate  14.Nh6+  gxh6  15.Qxh5  can be answered with  15...Qg5  .  14...Bxe5  when the d5-knight is also hanging. }
