{ With a balanced position. Our knight has a great outpost on e4. The correspondence game Galjé, H 2180- Raus, M ICCF 2021 continued  20.Bc2  Rad8  21.Bb3  Kh8  22.Rfe1  Qf7  and ended in a draw. }
