{ I prefer the bishop here - it defends f5 so that we can play ...Nf6. Also our bishop nicely restricts the knight on d4. }
19. Nc3 Nf6 20. Nxd5
{ Taking back the pawn because of the pin on the a2-g8 diagonal. } 20... Kh8
{ The game soon ended in a draw in ½-½ Petersons, I 2342 - Szymanski, R 2374 ICCF 2021 }
