Bd3 { A natural move, but actually a big mistake. } 10... cxd4
{ I was soon 2 pawns up in the blitz game 0-1 Postny, E 2557 - Parligras, M 2575 Warsaw blitz 2021. Note that White cannot play  11.cxd4  because of  11...Qc3+  winning material. }
