{ There were several ways to get compensation here. With ...a6 we want to play ...Nd7-b6. }
17. Bc4 Nd7
{ And ...Nb6 is next. Black has good compensation here. The white king is exposed, the b7-bishop and the e4-knight are excellent pieces. The compensation here is long-term - we'll not get the pawn back quickly, but we'll enjoy easy piece play.   A sample line goes  18.Rhc1  Nb6  19.Bb3  Na4  20.Bxa4  Qxa4  21.Kf1  Bd5  ,  followed by ...Rab8 with obvious compensation for the pawn. }
*

