{ Regardless of how White captures back by rook or pawn we play ...Bd5, trading the bishops. The position is about equal. The white rook was better off on e1. A sample line goes  16.Rxc3  Bd5  17.Bxd5  Rxc3  18.bxc3  exd5  . }
