17... Nxf3+ 18. Bxf3 Rhd8
{ We finally bring the last piece into play. Black's position is strategically sound, but there are still a few tactical details on the table.  A possible continuation is  19.Rcd1  e5  20.Rxd7+  Rxd7  21.Rxd7+  Kxd7  22.Qxf6  and now the precise move  22...Qc4  gives us good play. }
