{ Now it's time to trade all the rooks, and in the end the b7-pawn will be defended. }
20. Rxc1 Rc8 21. Rxc8 Bxc8
{ The endgame is equal.   Our king is more active and little by little we'll be able to activate the knight and bishop as well. For now ...Nc4 is a threat. }
