{ The only good square for the queen, otherwise ...Qa5 just wins a pawn. }
14... Qb6
{ We're offering a queen trade that White cannot accept because of the weak c3-pawn. }
15. Qa3 Qa5
{ This forces the queen trade, after which White still has some problems to solve. We can slowly push on the kingside by ...f6 and ...h5. The knight on e4 is very strong. }
